Author: khakitomatoes
Text: Yep I'm doublethinking HARD most of the time. Like, I look thin and normal and fat all at the same time. I also eat too much/too little, am sick and need help/perfectly fine... It's different parts of my brain thinking each thought and it's so frustrating. Can you just fucking DECIDE what I think of me and let me be in peace?
